#### e-Safe Ride Training — Day 1####

## Objective
- Build a simple Arduino circuit with an LED
- Make the LED blink using Arduino code

## Task 1 — Build Your First Circuit
**Components Used:**
- Arduino Uno R3
- 1 LED
- 1 220Ω resistor

**Circuit Connections:**
- LED long leg (anode) → Pin 13
- LED short leg (cathode) → 220Ω resistor → GND

