## Task 2 — Make the LED Blink
**Arduino Code:**
```cpp
void setup() {
  pinMode(13, OUTPUT);
}

void loop() {
  digitalWrite(13, HIGH); // LED ON
  delay(1000);
  digitalWrite(13, LOW);  // LED OFF
  delay(1000);
}
Notes:

LED blinks on/off every 1 second

Change delay() to make it blink faster/slower

